    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "doctors have tried everything. meds, injections, physical therapy... nothing works. it’s just a slow decay. sometimes i sit here and think about how much easier it would be if i could just find some peace, you know? like, if there was a way to just turn it all off so i didn't have to feel anything anymore. it feels like the only kind thing left to do for myself.",
